      • call

        public final DocumentsExportElementResponse call(String did,
                                                 WV wvType,
                                                 String wv,
                                                 String eid,
                                                 String format,
                                                 Number scale,
                                                 String mode)
                                          throws OnshapeException
        Calls exportElement method, Export the given element in STL or Parasolid (PS) formats; returns a 307 redirect.
        Parameters:
        did - Document ID
        wvType - Type of Workspace or Version
        wv - Workspace (w) or Version (v) ID
        eid - Element ID
        format - Export format: STL, PS (Default: null)
        scale - Scale for measurements (STL) (Default: null)
        mode - Type of file: text, binary (STL) (Default: null)
        Returns:
        Response object
        Throws:
        OnshapeException - On HTTP or serialization error
